data.message:
《潮州节2016》再次与你相约。倒数四天！海内外潮州美食尽在这里，我们就等你来一同参与其盛、品尝美味佳肴！
.
凡是于12月8日前购票者，即可享有10%的提前购票优惠，只需9元便能购得入门票！约定你哦！
Tickets now on sale! Enjoy a 10% early-bird discount when you get your ticket (Standard Price @ $10) from now till 8 Dec 2016.
.
Tickets are available at:
● Chui Huay Lim Club (醉花林俱乐部)
● Nam Hwa Opera Ltd - Official FB (南华儒剧社)
● 新加坡潮州八邑会馆 Teochew Poit Ip Huay Kuan (新加坡潮州八邑会馆)
● BreadTalk® Singapore
● Din Tai Fung Singapore
● Food Republic Singapore
● SK Jewellery
● Thye Moh Chan Singapore
● Toast Box Singapore
● www.sistic.com.sg  (available from 6 Dec onwards)
.
《#潮州节2016》Teochew Festival Singapore
Date: 9 - 18 Dec 2016
Time: 9 Dec (1pm - 9pm)
10 - 18 Dec (10:30am - 9pm)
Venue: Sands Expo and Convention Centre, Level 1 Hall A
